From cou.: 14 Contact angle measurements were also performed on the two polymer surfaces to see if the plasma treatment affects the hydrophilicity/hydrophobicity of the surface. Static water contact angles were measured using a CAM 100 optical contact meter (KSV Instruments). The PS and PI surfaces were the same surfaces used in lap shear measurements, and they were prepared the same way as previously stated.
From Soup: 14 Contact angle measurements were also performed on the two polymer surfaces to see if the plasma treatment affects the hydrophilicity/hydrophobicity of the surface. Static water contact angles were measured using a CAM 100 optical contact meter (KSV Instruments). The PS and PI surfaces were the same surfaces used in lap shear measurements, and they were prepared the same way as previously stated.
