From cou.: 16 For the plasma treatment experiments, the plasma was generated with the PE-50, Plasma Etch, Capacitively Coupled Plasma chamber. The treatment was 100 s, the pressure was 200 mTorr, and the generator was 400 W 50 KHz Continuously Variable Power Supply with Automatic Matching Network. Voltage used was 20 kV.
From Soup: 16 For the plasma treatment experiments, the plasma was generated with the PE-50, Plasma Etch, Capacitively Coupled Plasma chamber. The treatment was 100 s, the pressure was 200 mTorr, and the generator was 400 W 50 KHz Continuously Variable Power Supply with Automatic Matching Network. Voltage used was 20 kV.
